07 February, 2022

Source: vignettes/00_logo/00_logo.Rmd
00_logo.Rmd

This example describes the process to create the TERMS logo.

  1. Download the font bpdots
  2. Write TERMS with this font

  1. Overlap circles on top, save as svg
  2. Import coordinates and radii
